{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfa7\u00a0<strong>RippleFX\u00a0</strong>revolutionizes music visualization, transforming sound into a breathtaking visual masterpiece. Immerse yourself in your music like never before with a next-generation visualizer that\u2019s interactive, customizable, and endlessly creative. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920750/extras/Furball.gif?t=1734820337\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83c\udfb5 Dynamic Interaction</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Particles come alive, dancing and swaying to your music\u2019s rhythm. Customize their colors, speed, and behavior to match your vibe. RippleFX turns you from a spectator into a creator, letting you shape the visuals in real time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920750/extras/Interaction.gif?t=1734820337\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83c\udf99\ufe0f <u>Real-Time Microphone Input</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From vocals to instruments, RippleFX reacts seamlessly to live sounds. Your voice or instrument becomes the conductor of a stunning visual performance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83d\udca1\u00a0<u>Total Customization</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft your unique visual style with fine-tuned control over particle emitters and effects. Save your favorite setups as presets for quick access.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920750/extras/Customization.gif?t=1734820337\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u2728\u00a0<u><strong>Features</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Plug-and-play functionality</strong>: Start instantly, no complicated setup.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Saveable presets</strong>: Keep your favorite setups ready to go.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Microphone integration</strong>: Experience live, interactive reactions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Real-time adjustments</strong>: Shape visuals as they happen.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Interactive particle effects</strong>: Customize color, speed, and behavior.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fine-tuned emitter control</strong>: Perfect your visual masterpiece.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>RippleFX</i> isn\u2019t just a visualizer\u2014it\u2019s your creative playground. Take your music experience to the next level. \ud83c\udf0c                              </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920750/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734820337","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920750/page.bg.jpg?t=1734820337","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920750/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734820337","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920750/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734820337","content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3361680,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfa7\u00a0<strong>RippleFX\u00a0</strong>revolutionizes music visualization, transforming sound into a breathtaking visual masterpiece. Immerse yourself in your music like never before with a next-generation visualizer that\u2019s interactive, customizable, and endlessly creative. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920750/extras/Furball.gif?t=1734820337\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83c\udfb5 Dynamic Interaction</strong></p><p class